[% WRAPPER h2_section id = "what-i-learned" title = "What I taught (and learned from) Internet/social media creators (on YouTube and other Internet outlets)" %]

<ol>

<li>
<p>
<a href="[% base_path %]humour/Queen-Padme-Tales/Queen-Padme-Tales--Queen-Amidala-vs-the-Klingon-Warriors.html#dedication">Be confident</a> - your early works do not have to be perfect.
</p>

<p>
Women and girls can also be confident and brave.
</p>

<ol>

<li>
<p>
In general, avoid perfectionism. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perfection#Paradoxes">Perfection is in imperfection.</a>. <a href="http://catb.org/~esr/writings/cathedral-bazaar/cathedral-bazaar/ar01s04.html">“Release early”</a> when you are happy enough with your work.
</p>
</li>

</ol>

</li>

<li>
<p>
You can be both competent and resourceful <b>and</b> socially capable, sexy,
and sexually assertive.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
Encourage competitors and even give them publicity and advice.
( <a href="[% base_path %]humour/human-hacking/human-hacking-field-guide-v2/homecoming_queen.xhtml">reference</a> )
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
<a href="http://shlomifishswiki.branchable.com/Encourage_criticism_and_try_to_get_offended/">Encourage criticism</a>,
don't <a href="http://shlomifishswiki.branchable.com/Never_Try_to_Please_Everyone/">try to please everyone</a>,
but realise that you're awesome.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
<a href="[% base_path %]philosophy/philosophy/putting-cards-on-the-table-2019-2020/indiv-nodes/make-your-own-kind-of-music.xhtml">"Make your own kind of music"</a>:
</p>

<ol>

<li>
<p>
On the other hand, it is OK to
<a href="[% base_path %]meta/nav-blocks/blocks/#commercial_fanfic_initiative_sect">build upon, mash up, or even parody others' efforts</a>.
</p>
</li>

<li>
<p>
Similarly <a href="https://twitter.com/shlomif/status/1482599505975463943">allow
and encourage derivatives</a>.
</p>
</li>

</ol>

</li>

<li>
<p>
Be a geek: a <a href="[% base_path %]humour/fortunes/paul-graham.html">neo-amateur</a> - someone who loves his work, but might accept large monetary pledges.
( <a href="[% base_path %]humour/fortunes/show.cgi?id=prioritizing-money">It will likely yield more money, anyway.</a> )
</p>

</li>

<li>

<p>
Don't worry about fans or haters “diluting your brand”. <a href="https://www.shlomifish.org/meta/FAQ/may_i_prepare_a_derivative.xhtml">Hunting down copyright "violations"</a>
is usually a waste of time, energy, and love. Most violators are giving you free publicity anyway.
</p>

