<a href="https://www.shlomifish.org/philosophy/culture/case-for-commercial-fan-fiction/indiv-nodes/be_communicative.xhtml">Be communicative:</a>
</p>

<blockquote cite="">

[% INCLUDE avoiding_non_helpful_criticism %]

</blockquote>

