<li>
<p>
Expect that everyone, and everything will improve -
<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pygmalion_effect">the Pygmalion effect</a>
vs. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golem_effect">the Golem effect</a>.
